sql: SELECT COUNT(address_id), address_details FROM Addresses WHERE address_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Delivery_Route_Locations AS c WHERE Addresses.address_id = c.location_address_id) ORDER BY address_details DESC
SELECT l.actual_order_id, l.product_id FROM Actual_Order_Products AS l WHERE  l.actual_order_id >= 56 GROUP BY l.product_id
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT k.product_id), k.product_id FROM Actual_Order_Products AS k WHERE k.actual_order_id = 65 GROUP BY k.product_id ORDER BY k.product_id DESC
SELECT address_id, zip_postcode, city FROM Addresses WHERE  address_id > 74 GROUP BY city HAVING MIN(address_id) < 89 LIMIT 6

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT T1.actual_order_id), T4.product_id FROM Actual_Order_Products AS T1 JOIN Regular_Order_Products AS T2 ON T1.product_id = T2.product_id JOIN Regular_Orders AS T3 ON T2.regular_order_id = T3.regular_order_id JOIN Products AS T4 ON T2.product_id = T4.product_id JOIN Actual_Orders AS T5 ON T1.actual_order_id = T5.actual_order_id WHERE T3.regular_order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND T1.actual_order_id = 96 LIMIT 1
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT regular_order_id), COUNT(DISTINCT distributer_id) FROM Regular_Orders WHERE regular_order_id > 51;
SELECT route_name, other_route_details FROM Delivery_Routes GROUP BY route_name, other_route_details;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT product_name), product_name, product_description FROM Products WHERE product_price <= 69 GROUP BY product_description HAVING COUNT(product_name) < 35 LIMIT 3
SELECT COUNT(location_address_id), route_id FROM Delivery_Route_Locations WHERE  location_address_id = 20 ORDER BY route_id ASC LIMIT 4
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT product_id) FROM Actual_Order_Products WHERE  actual_order_id = 40
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT truck_details), COUNT(DISTINCT truck_licence_number), truck_licence_number FROM Trucks WHERE truck_id = 71 GROUP BY truck_licence_number ORDER BY truck_licence_number ASC;
SELECT k.product_id FROM Actual_Order_Products AS k WHERE  k.actual_order_id = 100 GROUP BY k.product_id ORDER BY k.product_id DESC
SELECT MAX(truck_id) FROM Trucks WHERE truck_id > 9;

SELECT AOP.product_id, P.product_price FROM Regular_Order_Products ROP JOIN Actual_Order_Products AOP ON ROP.product_id = AOP.product_id JOIN Products P ON ROP.product_id = P.product_id WHERE AOP.product_id > 31 GROUP BY AOP.product_id HAVING SUM(AOP.product_id) > 3 ORDER BY AOP.product_id DESC LIMIT 9
SELECT order_status_code FROM Actual_Orders JOIN Regular_Orders ON Regular_Orders.regular_order_id = Actual_Orders.regular_order_id WHERE  Actual_Orders.regular_order_id != 84

SELECT COUNT(Products.product_id), AVG(Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id), COUNT(DISTINCT Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id), Products.product_price FROM Actual_Order_Products JOIN Products ON Actual_Order_Products.product_id = Products.product_id WHERE Products.product_price BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Products.product_price IN (SELECT product_price FROM Products AS d WHERE d.product_price BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND d.product_price < 93 LIMIT 8) GROUP BY Products.product_price, Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id, Actual_Order_Products.product_id HAVING MIN(Products.product_price) <= 56 ORDER BY Products.product_price DESC

SELECT address_type, customer_name FROM Customer_Addresses JOIN Customers ON Customers.customer_id = Customer_Addresses.customer_id WHERE Customer_Addresses.customer_id = 36 GROUP BY address_type, customer_name

SELECT Regular_Order_Products.regular_order_id, Actual_Orders.order_status_code FROM Regular_Order_Products JOIN Regular_Orders ON Regular_Order_Products.regular_order_id = Regular_Orders.regular_order_id JOIN Actual_Orders ON Regular_Orders.regular_order_id = Actual_Orders.regular_order_id JOIN Customers ON Regular_Orders.distributer_id = Customers.customer_id WHERE Regular_Orders.regular_order_id <= 22;
SELECT y.address_id FROM Addresses AS y WHERE  y.address_id > 33 LIMIT 2

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT order_status_code), order_status_code FROM Actual_Order_Products JOIN Actual_Orders ON Actual_Orders.actual_order_id = Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id WHERE product_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND actual_order_date NOT IN (SELECT actual_order_date FROM Actual_Orders WHERE regular_order_id = 22) LIMIT 5

SELECT w.regular_order_id FROM Actual_Orders AS w WHERE w.actual_order_id != 72 OR order_status_code IN (SELECT order_status_code FROM Actual_Orders AS e WHERE e.regular_order_id <= 44 LIMIT 3) ORDER BY w.regular_order_id DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT location_name), location_code FROM Delivery_Route_Locations WHERE route_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR route_id IN (SELECT route_id FROM Delivery_Routes) ORDER BY location_code DESC;
SELECT distributer_id FROM Regular_Orders WHERE distributer_id IN (SELECT distributer_id FROM Regular_Orders WHERE  regular_order_id = 34) ORDER BY distributer_id DESC
SELECT T2.actual_order_id FROM Delivery_Route_Locations AS T1 JOIN Order_Deliveries AS T2 ON T1.location_code = T2.location_code WHERE T2.driver_employee_id <= 68 LIMIT 10

SELECT MIN(driver_employee_id), employee_phone FROM Order_Deliveries JOIN Employees ON Order_Deliveries.driver_employee_id = Employees.employee_id WHERE delivery_date > (SELECT AVG(delivery_date) FROM Order_Deliveries WHERE actual_order_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10) ORDER BY employee_phone ASC

SELECT Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id, order_status_code FROM Actual_Order_Products JOIN Actual_Orders ON Actual_Orders.actual_order_id = Actual_Order_Products.actual_order_id WHERE  Actual_Orders.actual_order_id != 80 ORDER BY Actual_Orders.actual_order_id ASC LIMIT 4

SELECT T1.product_name FROM Products AS T1 JOIN Actual_Order_Products AS T2 ON T1.product_id = T2.product_id WHERE EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM Actual_Order_Products WHERE actual_order_id = 73 AND T1.product_id = product_id) ORDER BY T1.product_name ASC
